Exxaro Resources Says Its Six-Month Profit to Show a ‘Strong Improvement’

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-04T05:09:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/exxaro-resources-says-its-six-month-profit-to-show-a-strong-improvement-.html
Exxaro Resources Ltd. (EXX)  said its
consolidated net operating profit for the six months to June 30
is expected to show a “strong improvement” from a year
earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
